  "StockRole": "Experimental Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Banzai is an experimental Draconis Combine BattleMech designed to be a close-in brawler with a deadly sting. Utilizing a mix of Inner Sphere and Clan technology, the 'Mech is built around the MAL-1K Mauler's Endo Steel chassis and powered by a massive 360-rated XL fusion engine, augmented by the inclusion of both MASC and a Supercharger. As a result, the Banzai is capable of reaching speeds of 100 km/h in brief bursts. Seventeen and half tons of standard armor allow the 'Mech to weather an incredible volume of fire as it advances, while fifteen Double Heat Sinks ensure the Banzai is able to fire its ranged weaponry as it closes with its intended target. For the pilot's protection from the 'Mech's booby trap, the Banzai is equipped with a Full-Head Ejection System.",
